 <br>
DIVINE MIGHT QUEST<br>
Classes:Paladin<br>
Description:<br>
這是一個得到神聖之力魔法的任務。他只能被五十級以上的聖騎士完成。他啟始在於迷宮看守者，Diggs Duggin，他在迷宮附近巡邏而且當你和他打招呼，他將會說：'Ail, dere! Ain'tcha a sight fer me sore eyes! I knows dat we're strangers an' all, but might I ask a [boon] of ye?<br>
<br>
問他：「what boon?」接著他會回答&quot;Well, me pickaxe is blunted awfully bad and me ale supplies are dangerously low. If'n ye would be kind enough t' get me a new pick and a couple o' bottles o' dwarven ale, I would be f'rever in yer debt.&quot;<br>
<br>
給他一個Pick(在Kaladim Bank門內的商人可找到)和二個Dwarven Ales(不要堆在一起，每個空格放一個)<br>
<br>
Diggs Duggun喝一瓶Ales並打了個大嗝後說： &quot;By Brell's Beard! Yer a lifesaver, ya are! 'ere, take dis bone I've found 'ere in dis maze. Looks human ta me and I'm thinkin that a proper burial is in order. Freeport's the closest place dat has one o Marr's temples. I'm thinkin dis was one o' his Holy Knights by da look o' da tattered tunic I found it wrapped in. I'm thinkin Valeron might be havin an interest in it.&quot;<br>
<br>
Diggs 給你“a dusty old leg bone“它是no drop 和lore。現在去找北Freeport之Hall of Truth 的聖騎士NPC Valeron Dushire。<br>
<br>
當你和Valeron Dushire打招呼他將會說I am Sir Valeron Dushire, leader of the order of the Knights of Truth. If your soul shines with purity and strength, I urge you to join our order. The might of Mithaniel Marr stands behind all who join. Soon that might will help us free this city from the tyranny of the [Freeport Militia].'<br>
如果你問「who is Diggs Duggun？」<br>
<br>
他將回答：'According to this crest on the tunic, you have recovered one of the bones of a lost Paladin [Hero].'<br>
<br>
再問「what hero？」<br>
<br>
而他將說：'His name has been long lost but his legend lives on in every young knight who aspires to continue his fight. He attempted to quell an evil that resided within Kithicor, perverting nature itself. Much to his relief, it was an earthly foe he fought against and not a denizen summoned from the planes of evil. Then, suddenly, he was surrounded by dozens of dark elves. He was captured and taken to the Dead to be experimented upon and had his soul twisted by vile necromantic magics. Then the Tier'Dal cast his remains to the winds. Where they landed, no one knew, until now. You have found one of his bones. I hereby charge you with a Holy Quest to bring this Heros bones back for a burial with honors. Do you [accept], knight?<br>
<br>
當然你將說：「I accept」<br>
<br>
而Valeron將繼續說：'Good! I knew you would. It is one of the highest honors one can receive. Your quest will not be easy for I know not where his other bones lay. A spy of ours within Neriak was able to surmise that six of his bones along with his sword and shield were scattered throughout Norrath. You must search far and wide to find the remaining pieces, as you already have one.. Do not give up. It is now your sacred duty. Once you have retrieved all eight pieces, come back to me and inform me that you [have all the bones].<br>
<br>
接著，你需要找到6個bones，一個盾，一把劍和棺材。<br>
<br>
這是這些物回和它們的位置：<br>
1.Dusty Skull - Mino caves in Steamfont in Meldrath's room (在Steamfont 的Mino caves的Meldrath’s room)<br>
<br>
2.Dusty Leg - You receive from talking to the dwarf in Beholder's Maze (你從和在Beholder’s Maze的矮人談話中得來)<br>
<br>
3.Dusty Ribcage - The Garden in Castle MM (Castle MM的花園)<br>
<br>
4.Dusty Backbone - Ghost Room Pit in Unrest (Unrest的Ghost Room pit)<br>
<br>
5.Dusty Jawbone - Underwater Ice Cave in Everfrost (Everfrost的水下Ice Cave)<br>
<br>
6.Dusty Finger Bones - Phinigel's Room in Kedge Keep (KK的Phinigel’s Room)<br>
<br>
7.The sword is found in the mines of Kaladim in the water (在Kaladim的礦坑發現，在水中)<br>
<br>
8.The shield is found on a ledge on right cliffs in Erudin from the docks(從Erudin的Dock開始沿著右方游,在懸崖旁的突出岩石上可找到盾牌)<br>
<br>
9.這個棺材從Ping Fizzlecutter得到。<br>
<br>
如果你說：「I have all the Bones」<br>
<br>
Valeron Dushire會說：「Excellect!You are indeed worthy to bear the title of Holy knight ! Now,about the coffin . I have spoken with ping Fizzlecutter , outside the weatern gates. Ask him about the Coffin and it is made , bring it to Simon Aldicott of Marr . I shall have Simon meet you by the lake in the commonlands after ping gives you the coffin . 」<br>
<br>
Ping need 多種Gems包含Diamond。(注意，要和Ping 談話，你要說：「Tell me about the coffin..」要兩個句點，要不他不會動作。<br>
<br>
為了要得到正確的Fire Emerald 給這個任務，你必須要去Firiona Vie並和Brisha Eyrestone說話！<br>
<br>
當你說：「what about the special fire emerald？」<br>
<br>
Brisha Fyrestone 說：「Why whould you want one of those？Not many people request them，expcept in special cases , even you with all your powers can’t tell the difference between them. Simply give Drake any fire emerald that you may have and he will make sure you get the special one.」<br>
<br>
然後去並帶著舊的fire emerald到Drake Mountainstorm，在他檢查這個fire emerald之後，他伸手到他的小袋子並拿給你另一個。<br>
<br>
他將接者說：「There you go , it doesn’t look special , but it is . If uou don’t believe me I’ii take another look at it .  Just remember this special fire emerald only have one purpose!」<br>
<br>
這個gem已被鑑定，但是不要堆在一起！<br>
